{"tid":2296592,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"父母均來自台灣!法學教授加入拜登交接團隊","createTime":"2020-11-22T14:56:50.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-30T10:35:56.000Z","uid":75656,"like":0,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"1efe0c72c3aadb8cabc83e71e3834febeb3b67a9","tid":2296592,"uid":75656,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-22T14:56:50.000Z","msg":"美國《世界日報》報導，父母均來自台灣的聖塔克拉拉大學（Santa Clara University）法學教授錢為德（Colleen V. Chien），已接受拜登團隊委任加入美國商務部交接團隊，成為團隊中唯一台裔學者，也是唯一華裔人士。報導指，在南加州生長的錢為德，是全美知名智慧財產權法專家，未來若加入拜登政府的智財權政策上發揮重要影響力。<br />\n<br />\n報導指，錢為德2013年就曾因學術成就卓越，被歐巴馬政府任命為白宮智財權與創新首席科技長的資深顧問。當時她的工作範圍，包括推動開放資料政策與增加兒科愛滋病藥物通路等。她曾在多次在眾院司法委員會等多個聯邦機構作證，並在智慧財產權、創新、隱私權、公民自由和開放政府等多個領域的公共政策制定扮演重要角色。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://tw.appledaily.com/international/20201119/DSQMOBMKBNFODNN23GJ7IWUULI/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20201119%2FDSQMOBMKBNFODNN23GJ7IWUULI%2F&d=icC9UeWzMg70WCHWfTItT%2B6cow1LS9WQT%2BeJ8I%2F17x8%3D&h=6010d25a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20201119%2FDSQMOBMKBNFODNN23GJ7IWUULI%2F&h=5efbc59d\" target=\"_blank\">https://tw.appledaily.com/international/20201119/DSQMOBMKBNFODNN23GJ7IWUULI/</a>"},{"pid":"e415fbc32bbd7c3a4fbaeffab174f87001aba85d","tid":2296592,"uid":14918,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-22T15:17:09.000Z","msg":"搵台灣人出賣台灣<br />\n好撚陰險<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8b2fe15466472a6c96c30f0a3b58080fb3961bd9","tid":2296592,"uid":26752,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-22T15:26:13.000Z","msg":"台奸"},{"pid":"adb97714fd695487520f11604ac43fcf5aa6c7d9","tid":2296592,"uid":370409,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-30T10:35:56.000Z","msg":"MILF<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}